Spence Lee - Spend My Days (2023) directed by Medet. A masterful mv with eye popping transitions throughout. 👁️🍭

1. Projections + masking collage
2. Trucking shot transition wipes
3. Arc + super zoom + object portal 
4. Super zoom + object portal
5. Transition wipes
6. Super zoom to match split
7. Object portal (back window)
8. Object portal (boombox)
9. Aspect ratio switch
10. Reflection shot (dolly zoom)+ Dutch angle

The collage shot is actually layered over a practical projection, which has been projected onto the underbelly of the bridge. And if you recognize the bridge, it’s the same one from Migos ‘Bad and Boujee’ 

A decent amount was shot on iPhone. 🔥🔥🔥
